name: Bizcard
tag_list: business-cards, postcards, magnets, design-services, direct-mail, green-seal, green-printing, eco-friendly
overview:
Bizcard is an eco-friendly print solutions company based in Scottsdale, AZ. Bizcard serves businesses of all sizes, focusing in particular on small to medium-sized companies.

Since its founding, Bizcard has been working on developing environmentally friendly printing solutions. This effort includes using primarily post-consumer paper, eliminating damaging photo chemicals from the printing process and purchasing materials from GreenSeal certified companies.

Bizcard’s reputation has been built primarily on the strength of its business cards, including several unique types in addition to their standard line. However, Bizcard also features a number of other products and services in the realm of print collateral and marketing resources.
